Class Matches

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.model.Matches

  • public class Matches
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the major components of a match: initial word, semantic relation and repaired word This is used to display the matches in a TreeTableView in DisplayMatchesController
    Author:
    Tom Feraud
